\par }{\b\f0\fs20 Resist Fear:}{\f0\fs20  In response to a fear effect, you can make an Autohypnosis check on your next action even if you\rquote 
ve been overcome by fear. A successful check grants you another saving throw with a +4 morale bonus to resist the fear effect.
\par }{\b\f0\fs20 Memorize:}{\f0\fs20  You can attempt to me
morize a long string of numbers, a long passage of verse, or other particularly difficult piece of information. Each successful check allows you to memorize up to 250 words or the equivalent of what could be comfortably contained on an 8 1/2-by-11-inch sh
eet of paper. You always retain this information; however, you can only recall it with a successful Autohypnosis check.
\par }{\b\f0\fs20 Tolerate Poison:}{\f0\fs20  In response to being poisoned, you can make an Autohypnosis check on your next action. A successful check grants you a +4 morale bonus on your saving throw to resist the poison\rquote s secondary damage.
