you can choose not to perform the strenuous action. If you do perform the strenuous action after failing the check, you take 1 point of damage, as normal.
\par }{\b\f0\fs20 Try Again?:}{\f0\fs20  For resist fear and memorize, you can make a check once per round. You can\rquote t try again to tolerate poison. You can\rquote t try again in the same round for willpower.
