The Acolyte gains a number of action points equal to 6 + one-half her character level, rounded down, every time she attains a new level in this class.
\par }\pard\plain \s3\ql \li0\ri0\keepn\nowidctlpar\faauto\outlinelevel2\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f5\fs20\cf1\up3\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f0\up0 Class Skills
