. She gets a +4 bonus on Concentration checks made to cast a spell while on the defensive.
\par }\pard\plain \s3\ql \li0\ri0\keepn\nowidctlpar\faauto\outlinelevel2\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f5\fs20\cf1\up3\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f0\up0 Turn or Rebuke Magical Beast
